Yes.

00:18:45.760 --> 00:18:51.119
So in the cells, we do have full shiny input output support.

00:18:51.839 --> 00:18:58.640
So it was really fun to have a cell of the table end up being a full plotly plot.

00:19:00.160 --> 00:19:05.040
And, you know, it was kind of like trying to figure out what's capable and not if we should.

